{
  "page": "Sharra Arryn",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the legendary hero of the riverlands, see <a href=\"/index.php/Sharra_the_Witch_Queen\" title=\"Sharra the Witch Queen\">Sharra the Witch Queen</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><img alt=\"No image.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1d/No_image.svg/50px-No_image.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1d/No_image.svg/75px-No_image.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1d/No_image.svg/100px-No_image.svg.png 2x\" /></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Queen</span><br />Sharra Arryn<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> the Flower of the Mountain</span></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\"><img alt=\"House Arryn.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/50px-House_Arryn.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/75px-House_Arryn.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/100px-House_Arryn.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Sharra_Arryn.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Sharra Arryn.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/96/Sharra_Arryn.png/350px-Sharra_Arryn.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"/images/9/96/Sharra_Arryn.png 1.5x\" /></a><div>Sharra Arryn as depicted in <i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i>: <i>Histories &amp; Lore</i>.</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nThe Flower of the Mountain</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Kingship\" title=\"Kingship\">Queen</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Regent\" title=\"Regent\">Regent</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\">House Arryn</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Valemen\" title=\"Valemen\">Valemen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_before_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_37_Before_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years before Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">37&#160;BC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li>King/Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Ronnel_Arryn_(king)\" title=\"Ronnel Arryn (king)\">Ronnel Arryn</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Jonos_Arryn\" title=\"Jonos Arryn\">Jonos Arryn</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Sharra Arryn</b>, known as <b>the Flower of the Mountain</b>, was <a href=\"/index.php/Kingship\" title=\"Kingship\">Queen</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Regent\" title=\"Regent\">Regent</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingdom_of_Mountain_and_Vale\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Kingdom of Mountain and Vale\">Kingdom of Mountain and Vale</a>, ruling in the name of her son, the boy-king <a href=\"/index.php/Ronnel_Arryn_(king)\" title=\"Ronnel Arryn (king)\">Ronnel Arryn</a>, during the <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_Conquest\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"War of Conquest\">invasion</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a> by <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#The_War_of_Conquest\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">The War of Conquest</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sharra_Arryn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>In her youth, Sharra was regarded as one of the most beautiful women of Westeros, known as the \"the Flower of the Mountain\".<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Sharra married the <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_Mountain_and_Vale\" title=\"King of Mountain and Vale\">King of Mountain and Vale</a> and had two sons with him, <a href=\"/index.php/Ronnel_Arryn_(king)\" title=\"Ronnel Arryn (king)\">Ronnel</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Jonos_Arryn\" title=\"Jonos Arryn\">Jonos Arryn</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Sharra was widowed when Ronnel was only a boy, and so rule of the <a href=\"/index.php/Vale_of_Arryn\" title=\"Vale of Arryn\">Vale of Arryn</a> fell to Sharra.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_War_of_Conquest\">The War of Conquest</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sharra_Arryn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The War of Conquest\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\" style=\"width:520px;\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\">\n<ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-packed\" style=\"margin:0px; text-align:left\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\" style=\"width: 250px\"><div style=\"width: 250px\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\" style=\"width: 248px;\"><div style=\"margin:0px auto;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Visenya_conquers_the_Vale_pt_4_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Visenya conquers the Vale pt 4 by Jota Saraiva.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/57/Visenya_conquers_the_Vale_pt_4_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg/372px-Visenya_conquers_the_Vale_pt_4_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg\" width=\"248\" height=\"248\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/57/Visenya_conquers_the_Vale_pt_4_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg/558px-Visenya_conquers_the_Vale_pt_4_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/57/Visenya_conquers_the_Vale_pt_4_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg/744px-Visenya_conquers_the_Vale_pt_4_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg 2x\" /></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\" style=\"width: 250px\"><div style=\"width: 250px\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\" style=\"width: 248px;\"><div style=\"margin:0px auto;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Visenya_conquers_the_Vale_pt_5_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Visenya conquers the Vale pt 5 by Jota Saraiva.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/73/Visenya_conquers_the_Vale_pt_5_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg/372px-Visenya_conquers_the_Vale_pt_5_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg\" width=\"248\" height=\"248\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/73/Visenya_conquers_the_Vale_pt_5_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg/558px-Visenya_conquers_the_Vale_pt_5_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/73/Visenya_conquers_the_Vale_pt_5_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg/744px-Visenya_conquers_the_Vale_pt_5_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg 2x\" /></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">Sharra confronts <a href=\"/index.php/Visenya_Targaryen\" title=\"Visenya Targaryen\">Visenya Targaryen</a>, only to find her son, young king <a href=\"/index.php/Ronnel_Arryn\" title=\"Ronnel Arryn\">Ronnel Arryn</a>, sitting on Visenya's knee, wishing to fly upon her <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragon</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Vhagar\" title=\"Vhagar\">Vhagar</a>. Art by Jota Saraiva ©</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>After <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon I Targaryen</a> launched his <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_Conquest\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"War of Conquest\">invasion</a> and made his intentions known to the rulers of the <a href=\"/index.php/Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Seven Kingdoms\">seven independent kingdoms</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a>, Sharra sent a portrait of herself to him and offered her hand in marriage with the condition Aegon would make Ronnel his heir. Though it is unknown if Aegon replied, he did apparently reject her proposal, as he already had two queens, and Sharra was ten years older than him, no longer as beautiful as she was in her youth.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The Vale scored a victory against the invaders in a <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_in_the_waters_off_Gulltown\" title=\"Battle in the waters off Gulltown\">battle in the waters off Gulltown</a>, though the Arryn fleet was burned afterwards by Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Visenya_Targaryen\" title=\"Visenya Targaryen\">Visenya Targaryen</a> and her <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragon</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Vhagar\" title=\"Vhagar\">Vhagar</a>. With the Arryn fleet destroyed, the <a href=\"/index.php/Three_Sisters\" title=\"Three Sisters\">Sistermen</a> revolted against Arryn rule.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>As other regions of Westeros fell to Aegon, Sharra strengthened the defenses of <a href=\"/index.php/Gulltown\" title=\"Gulltown\">Gulltown</a>, amassed the Vale army at the <a href=\"/index.php/Bloody_Gate\" title=\"Bloody Gate\">Bloody Gate</a>, and tripled the garrisons of <a href=\"/index.php/Stone_(waycastle)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Stone (waycastle)\">Stone</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Snow_(waycastle)\" title=\"Snow (waycastle)\">Snow</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Sky\" title=\"Sky\">Sky</a>. However, Visenya bypassed these hosts by flying up to the <a href=\"/index.php/Eyrie\" title=\"Eyrie\">Eyrie</a> upon Vhagar's back, and landed the dragon in its courtyard. When Sharra returned to the Eyrie, she found Ronnel sitting on Visenya's knee, staring up at Vhagar. The wonderstruck boy king asked his mother if he could go flying upon the dragon. But Visenya made no verbal threats, and neither did Sharra; the queens only smiled and exchanged courtesies. After Sharra bent the knee and surrendered the <a href=\"/index.php/Falcon_Crown\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Falcon Crown\">Falcon Crown</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\">House Arryn</a>, Ronnel's small <a href=\"/index.php/Crown\" title=\"Crown\">crown</a>, and her own regent's coronet, Ronnel flew with Visenya upon Vhagar around the summit of the <a href=\"/index.php/Giant%27s_Lance\" title=\"Giant&#39;s Lance\">Giant's Lance</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> \n</p><p>Rather than kings, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\">House Arryn</a> henceforth ruled as <a href=\"/index.php/Lords_of_the_Eyrie\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lords of the Eyrie\">Lords of the Eyrie</a>, Defenders of the Vale, and <a href=\"/index.php/Warden_of_the_East\" title=\"Warden of the East\">Wardens of the East</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale:_house_arryn.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_vale:_house_arryn.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sharra_Arryn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\">Unknown<br /><a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\">Arryn</a></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sharra</a></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td></tr><tr align=\"center\"><td style=\"border-right:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:1em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td><div style=\"width:1em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td></tr>\n<tr align=\"center